Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.46,0:36:17.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们将我们的 frac 从 0 增加到 1
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.86,0:36:31.12,English,,0,0,0,,Now this represents the the significant of 1.001
