Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.62,0:46:10.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在你可以应用此功能，你可以将此舍入到任何值
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.38,0:46:15.00,English,,0,0,0,,So in the last example we did it to the nearest dollar
