Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.40,0:46:59.78,English,,0,0,0,,So we would just round down to 7.89
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.40,0:46:59.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我们只需要向下舍入到 7.89
