Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.36,0:48:03.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,到下一个位置，九和一是零，九和一是 10，所以继续
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.24,0:48:10.48,English,,0,0,0,,And so 8+1=9,so the result is set of rounding up is 7.90
