Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.66,0:48:29.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后只需进行相加，这将给你最近的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.44,0:48:35.28,English,,0,0,0,,The nearest that will round you up to the nearest hundredth in this case
